libbc-core (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * Memory primitives: cache-line-aware copy/zero, SIMD equal/compare,
    NUL-bounded length, byte-find / last-byte-find.
  * Hash primitives: SHA-256 with runtime-dispatched SHA-NI fast path,
    CRC32C (Castagnoli) via SSE4.2.
  * Math primitives: overflow-safe add/multiply, clamp helpers.
  * CPU helpers: BC_UNUSED macro, CPUID feature-flag probes.
  * Full sanitizer coverage (asan / tsan / ubsan / memcheck) and
    cppcheck-clean sources.

 -- Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>  Sat, 18 Apr 2026 23:30:00 +0000
